Package structures.linear

Class Summary
LinkedList<T> This class implements a generic circular linked list (CLL).
List<T> This class implements a generic unordered list.
Merger This class implements "merging" operations union, intersection, and difference on two ordered lists.
Node<T> Helper class that implements linked list nodes.
OrderedList<T extends Comparable<T>> This class implements a generic ordered list.
Queue<T> This class implements a generic FIFO queue.
Stack<T> This class implements a generic LIFO stack.
 

Exception Summary
OrderViolationException This is a runtime exception thrown to indicate that an attempt is being made to violate the ordering of a structure.
